{"id":136,"date":"2020-01-02T01:41:47","date_gmt":"2020-01-02T01:41:47","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/?p=136"},"modified":"2021-05-23T00:04:28","modified_gmt":"2021-05-22T17:04:28","slug":"cac-hinh-thuc-lien-thong-cd-nganh-duoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/cac-hinh-thuc-lien-thong-cd-nganh-duoc\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c li\u00ean th\u00f4ng C\u0110 ng\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c\u00a0<strong>li\u00ean th\u00f4ng C\u0110 ng\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhu c\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 55 \/2012\/TT-BGD\u0110T ng\u00e0y 25 th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m 2012 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edfng B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i \u0110i\u1ec1u 12 T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o li\u00ean th\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o li\u00ean th\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh quy, \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o li\u00ean th\u00f4ng v\u1eeba l\u00e0m v\u1eeba h\u1ecdc. V\u00ec v\u1eady h\u1ecdc li\u00ean th\u00f4ng l\u00ean Cao \u0111\u1eb3ng D\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean:<\/p>\n<h2><b>Li\u00ean th\u00f4ng theo h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh quy<\/b><\/h2>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p TC D\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u1eddi gian t\u1ea1i c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c. Sinh vi\u00ean h\u1ec7 li\u00ean th\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh quy h\u1ecdc chung thi h\u1ebft m\u00f4n v\u00e0 thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p. Ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 lu\u1eadn v\u0103n t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111\u1ed3 \u00e1n t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi sinh vi\u00ean h\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh quy.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1178\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1178\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1178 lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cac-hinh-thuc-lien-thong-cd-nganh-duoc-136.jpg\" alt=\"D\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh quy\" width=\"700\" height=\"489\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cac-hinh-thuc-lien-thong-cd-nganh-duoc-136.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1178\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>D\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh quy<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc li\u00ean th\u00f4ng Cao \u0111\u1eb3ng D\u01b0\u1ee3c theo h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh quy c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n :<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"first\">C\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p TC ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c<\/li>\n<li>Tham d\u1ef1 thi tuy\u1ec3n li\u00ean th\u00f4ng do n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c<\/li>\n<li class=\"last\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 l\u00fd l\u1ecbch trong s\u1ea1ch<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><b>Hai li\u00ean th\u00f4ng C\u0110 ng\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c theo h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c v\u1eeba h\u1ecdc v\u1eeba l\u00e0m<\/b><\/h2>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u00ec thi nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c 1. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho m\u00ecnh.\u00a0 H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1edfi \u0111a s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng \u0103n vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb. V\u00ec mu\u1ed1n th\u0103ng ch\u1ee9c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng hay \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf trong c\u01a1 quan.<\/p>\n<h2><b>Li\u00ean th\u00f4ng theo h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb xa<\/b><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1179\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1179\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1179 lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cac-hinh-thuc-lien-thong-cd-nganh-duoc-136-1.jpg\" alt=\"H\u1ecdc d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129\" width=\"700\" height=\"498\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/cac-hinh-thuc-lien-thong-cd-nganh-duoc-136-1.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1179\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>H\u1ecdc d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc li\u00ean th\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc h\u1ecdc theo c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thi c\u1eed nh\u01b0 2 c\u00e1ch tr\u00ean m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n h\u1ed3 s\u01a1. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 nghe gi\u1ea3ng tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn qua m\u1ea1ng internet. V\u1eady v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc ngay t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh . V\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed \u0111i l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c\u00a0li\u00ean th\u00f4ng C\u0110 ng\u00e0nh d\u01b0\u1ee3c\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhu c\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c. T\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 55 \/2012\/TT-BGD\u0110T ng\u00e0y 25 th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m 2012 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edfng B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o quy \u0111\u1ecbnh&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":138,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[17],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/136"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=136"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/136\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":139,"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/136\/revisions\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/138"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu10.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=136"}